<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mn swạh yṭhr mn kl ạldẖnwb .. mn swạh ybạrk brgẖm ạlʿywb
 mn swạh yḥạrb ʿnnạ ạlḥrwb
 ạlqrạr- (hllwyạ hllwyạ ạlrb ṣạlḥuⁿ)3 .. (hllwyạ hllwyạ wḥdh yswʿ)3
 2- mn swạh mạt ky mạ yḥyynạ .. mn swạh ḥml kl ạ̉wjạʿnạ
 mn swạh qạm wạ̉qạmnạ
 3- mn swạh ysẖfy yḥl ạlqywd .. mn swạh yḍmn tḥqyq ạlwʿwd
 mn swạh yrfʿ fwq kl ạlsdwd</lyrics>
